name: Tier
wikiSummary: Tier (German for Animal) is the third track on the album Sehnsucht by Rammstein. It explores themes of incest and child abuse.
wikiText:
Tier (German for Animal) is the third track on the album Sehnsucht by Rammstein. It explores themes of incest and child abuse.
